{"tid":732552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊招募日大學畢業生投考見習督察   冀改善警察形象","createTime":"2018-07-07T04:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T16:11:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"32563a05d34bde5a42119281315ed6ad5416d98f","tid":732552,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"警隊舉行招募日，聘請見習督察、警員和輔警。<br />\n<br />\n有應屆大學畢業生投考見習督察，他希望透過宣傳或改善執法方式，改變外界對警察的形象。<br />\n<br />\n有大學畢業生認為，警隊的薪酬和福利吸引而報考，對於有警察被指打示威者或記者，他認為是個別事件，不應該因為這些負面新聞，影響有數萬人部門的形象。<br />\n<br />\n就讀大學三年級女學生投考輔警，她希望成為輔警後加深認識警察條例，例如警察使用胡椒噴霧的準則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%8A%95%E8%80%83%E8%A6%8B%E7%BF%92%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E5%86%80%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1-024742733.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%258B%259F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%25BF%2592%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E8%25B1%25A1-024742733.html&d=bfsb2Z%2BflDqDUoBqCQS%2FZjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=afd1dbf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%8A%95%E8%80%83%E8%A6%8B%E7%BF%92%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E5%86%80%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1-024742733.html</a><br />\n<br />\n要改善社團形象, 不如先加入.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370aea3525c272ee0ffe3a5109d57a289009500e","tid":732552,"uid":128972,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"讀完大學都唔識咩叫個別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /